title: Childhood "Blue Velvet" - Converse Red Light Sessions
description:
Get lost in dreamy Indie rock as London based Childhood perform Blue Velvet for their Converse Red Light Session.

This track will be on the album Lacuna to be released this summer of 2014 on Marathon Artists.
